author: Nintendo of America
description:
Fight against the Dark Hour and seal your fate in Persona 3 Reload on Nintendo Switch 2: https://ninten.do/6059t8Sab 
  
Step into the shoes of a transfer student thrust into an unexpected fate when entering the hour ‘hidden’ between one day and the next. Awaken an incredible power and chase the mysteries of the Dark Hour, fight for your friends, and leave a mark on their memories forever. 
 
#Persona3Reload #NintendoSwitch2
title: Persona 3 Reload – Launch Trailer – Nintendo Switch 2

author: Nintendo of America
description:
Wackadoo! Playtime with the Heeler crew is now bigger and better in Bluey: The Videogame on Nintendo Switch: https://ninten.do/6056tD2Cm 
 
There is so much to do in this new update! You can play as Muffin and Uncle Stripe, learn new rules to some favorite minigames, enjoy new unlockables, help out new characters such as Nana, Grandad, and Aunt Trixie, discover new collectibles, and more. 
 
#BlueyTheVideogame #NintendoSwitch
title: Bluey The Videogame – Update Launch Trailer – Nintendo Switch
